lead_paragraph: GREENWALD--Doris. We were blessed by your strength, devotion, generosity, wit and humor. You were one of a kind. We love you and will miss you always. Sam, Evan, Randi, Carolyn, Brett, Brooke, Riley and Isla 1/3
